The paper focuses on developing an interactive, social agent (health coach) that can coach people to learn new tasks, skills, and habits. The approach is model-based, and the coach is embodied in a smartphone application. The evaluation approach is task-centric, and the study focuses on promoting regular aerobic exercise. Based on these factors, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC), followed by Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Cybersecurity (cs.CYBER), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), and Machine Learning (cs.LG).
